{"tid":462371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知芝士腸係用咩整","createTime":"2017-11-08T13:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T14:04:08.000Z","uid":61695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b4c6b812d354dc21d0841c7a7e8bc367bdb4f7","tid":462371,"uid":61695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"岀面果層皮究竟係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627c620d17f1d1f69d56ead2f65a9e7022a2fd1d","tid":462371,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"Cellulose casing?"},{"pid":"a75114e78ebba7d781d18dbe77b351aa9ee18249","tid":462371,"uid":26899,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係愛呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"09b0f2bfef81629d4984590e7182a60c8ce4aba3","tid":462371,"uid":61695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cellulose casing?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁用咩整？"},{"pid":"260629f321c416eea712baf553d690d8ce09d57e","tid":462371,"uid":72943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:29:37.000Z","msg":"羊小腸 豬小腸"},{"pid":"5de7390caf2e427ecb2996d4f6ea05ee16980f95","tid":462371,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羊小腸 豬小腸</blockquote><br />\n動物casing冇咁脆"},{"pid":"1a4eccbf80b6154ebe71f4d9eeb13ddbf8d04717","tid":462371,"uid":61695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羊小腸 豬小腸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁高成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e98530484291f3557f1e2707345e5f84b6e8191","tid":462371,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你的鳩"},{"pid":"b7adc8025fc0ed75f5d80b40387dabcf002cfb53","tid":462371,"uid":4880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"1.天然腸衣：多使用豬、羊或牛的大小腸，這種腸衣因需手工加工生產，以將不必要的肌肉組織及腸入廢棄物去除，經過沖洗，剩下黏膜下層結締組織中的膠原蛋白纖維，再以鳳梨酵素嫩化，所以價格較高，且數量有限。全球每年要用掉天然腸衣，約100萬哩長左右，而我們的中式香腸便是使用豬腸腸衣。 <br />\n<br />\n2.膠原纖維腸衣：使用海藻酸纖維、花生蛋白及牛皮提煉的膠原纖維蛋白製成，為可食性人工腸衣，我們的小熱狗採用此種腸衣。 <br />\n<br />\n3.纖維素腸衣：其材質特別堅韌，可抗凍、印刷或陳列，為不可食的腸衣，食用前需剝除，多使用在維也納香腸、法蘭克福熱狗、燻腸等西式香腸。我們的西式火腿的外層便是此一系列的腸衣，剪開後再切片食用。 <br />\n<br />\n4.塑膠腸衣：其透氣性及透水性較差、保存性佳且價格便宜，是不可食的腸衣，以PVDC最有名，目前我們並未採用此類腸衣。"},{"pid":"f29917bba6e8f602dce896ab6285deda223eb608","tid":462371,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"condoms"},{"pid":"67d3029e6390996ca50041fc96c948d970f2f2a6","tid":462371,"uid":61695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你的鳩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b4134c5d7a2d683994b0f0747ded618a6e894b","tid":462371,"uid":61695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>condoms</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}